# Package Management Rules

- Use Yarn as the package manager for this project. All package management commands should use Yarn, not npm.
- The [package.json](mdc:package.json) file must be present and maintained.
- The [yarn.lock](mdc:yarn.lock) file must be present and kept up to date.
- Do not use npm commands or maintain a package-lock.json file.
